ML_Model/data/
ML_Model/models/

# If you'd rather keep the processed CSVs tracked (they're small and
# save re-running feature engineering), comment the line above out and
# use these two instead:
# ML_Model/data/raw/
# ML_Model/models/saved_models/
# ML_Model/models/scalers/
# ML_Model/models/plots/

